item.title: Making telporters?
item.dc:creator: @Java_Is_My_Bitch Java Is My Bitch™
item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

Sure.

Go to client.java, Open it, press CTRL-F

In the input box put:

public void TeleTo(String s, int level)

Then once there, scroll down and find:

if (s == “Annakarl”) {

Where it says…

    teleX = 3288; 
    teleY = 3886;

Change the 3288 and the 3886, to the X’s and Y’s of your new place.

And thats it.
